# Core invariants

- Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for task routing and import rules.
- Production types: `@ext/core/types/index.ts` only.
- Domains import `@ext/core/**` + own domain only; never cross-import domains.
- Core/UI-core domain lib: `@ext/domains/{target,walmart}/lib/index.ts` barrels only.
- Content scripts never open tabs — service worker does.
- Never add `cookies`, `webRequest`, or `<all_urls>` permissions.
- After service-worker/manifest changes: reload extension + refresh Discord, Target, Walmart tabs.
- Prefer pure logic in `extension/core/lib/*` or domain `lib/*` with Vitest; keep `chrome.*` in background/content layers.
- Run `npm test` and `npm run lint` before committing.
